  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.6.5">
<l>nīraḻalāy neṭunilaṉāy niṉṟāṉai yaṉṟarakkaṉ</l>
<l>ūraḻalā luṇṭāṉaik kaṇṭārpiṉ kāṇāmē</l>
<l>pēraḻalāyp peruvicumpāyp piṉmaṟaiyōr mantirattiṉ</l>
<l>āraḻalā luṇṭāṉaik kaṇṭatuteṉ ṉaraṅkattē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] beholding of the one who endures as water and fire,</l>
<l rend="indent">and as the wide earth,</l>
<l>The one who once consumed the demon city with fire -</l>
<l rend="indent">those, who [once] saw [it], then being without sight [of it],</l>
<l>The one who, being the great fire and the vast heavens, then ate [offerings]</l>
<l>By means of the fire imbued with the mantras of the Vedic experts,</l>
<l rend="indent">was in Araṅkam of the South.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
